text: St. Francois Township is the name of four townships in the U.S. state of Missouri: *St. Francois Township, Butler County, Missouri *St. Francois Township, Madison County, Missouri *St. Francois Township, Saint Francois County, Missouri *St. Francois Township, Wayne County, Missouri ==See also== *Saint-François (disambiguation) Category:Missouri township disambiguation pages
title: St. Francois Township
